<http://model.geneontology.org/ev_w_id_R-HSA-1638796_R-HSA-1638821_controller_BFO_0000051_UniProtKB_Q96FF9_R-HSA-1638796_R-HSA-1638821_component_Reactome_R-HSA-2500257>
